# Overview
**Task Tracker** is a simple web application that lets users add, complete, filter, and persist tasks in the browser using localStorage.  
The goal was to practice core web skills (HTML, CSS, JavaScript), build interactive UI, and deliver clean, documented code.

[Software Demo Video](https://youtu.be/xxxxxxxxxxx)

# Development Environment
- HTML, CSS, JavaScript (Vanilla)
- Visual Studio Code
- Git & GitHub
- No frameworks required

# Program Functionality
- Add tasks with title and priority
- Mark tasks as done/undone
- Edit and delete tasks
- Filter by status (all/open/done) and by priority (low/normal/high)
- Persistent storage with localStorage
- Responsive and accessible UI

# How to Run
1. Clone the repository  
2. Open `index.html` in your browser (or use VS Code Live Server)

